channel.title: My first model (without all my recolers XD)
channel.description: hi i now this shield may look epic ugly or something like it but this is my first model i've made by myself :D so i was hoping to hear what i gonna learn or what i can do better :D cuz that is the only way you can get pro :D so here it comes :o [img]http://www.imageurlhost.com/images/1u16u0ct83nsqerpbal0.jpg[/img] [img]http://www.imageurlhost.com/images/c26geothyodcd608xp8o.jpg[/img] [img]http://www.imageurlhost.com/images/v1mwtf5phy94ajb2rip7.jpg[/img] last one datmaker view :D and i dont want command like it sucks if you really need say something like that then say why you mean it sucks :mad:

item.title: My first model (without all my recolers XD)
item.dc:creator: @CoonHunter CoonHunter
item.description:
@CoonHunter wrote:

Dylan is right Arc, the only reasons you started with primitives is because i made a video tut, showing that yes, cubes can actually become a blade, and such. Please, do not insult a method that you once used, and were treated well for, your becoming a small bit full of yourself imo, because your models were never really made for quality, just speed, and color. Some of them weren’t even built for color.

@TOPIC - Well, i would have started with something a little different, but thats just me, we all gotta start somewhere right? Im glad to see someone new around here, some ‘fresh meat’ as i like to call it, rofl. As for the model, its not bad, i would say 7/10 for your first, only because i can see a missing face in the first pic, but its not bad, keep working at it.

item.title: My first model (without all my recolers XD)
item.dc:creator: @dylan_0789 dylan_0789
item.description:
@dylan_0789 wrote:

[quote=“The Arcanian, post:2, topic:327118”]It sucks!

Why?

  • It’s a Trace
  • Ugly edges, could be more smoother.
  • I would choose other colors
  • I would add more depth to it.

5/10 Just becuz it’s your first![/quote]
You can go easy on him. YOU were a tracer. YOU traced everything. YOU didnt like primitives. YOU thought they were stupid and useless.
YOU shouldnt insult the method you first used. I can, because I never used the trace method, and never plan to. Stop acting like your ‘the shit’ please…

About the model: Its OK for a first. Not amazing. Not the worst. As Arcanian said(in a mean way) “its just a trace”. Try primitive modelling. Oh, this would make an (ok) shield
